# Template Rule Propagation

This repository is a template. Keep agent rules reusable for downstream apps.

## Requirements

- Keep authoritative rules in `.cursor/rules/`.
- When rules change, update README guidance and sync utilities if needed.
- For apps generated from this template, ensure `.cursor/rules/` exists in the new repo.

## Operational fallback

If scaffold tooling skips dotfiles, copy rules manually or run:

`npm run sync:cursor-rules -- <target-app-path>`
